description:
'''Digicore''' (originally known as '''draincore''') is a [[microgenre]] of [[hip-hop]] and [[electronic music]] that developed alongside [[hyperpop]] in the late 2010s to early 2020s. The genre is typically made up of artists that share stylistic similarities to [[Drain Gang]] and [[100 gecs]], rather than the "[[bubblegum bass]]" musicians signed to the label [[PC Music]].

Notable acts include [[Jane Remover]], [[d0llywood1]], [[Whethan]], [[aldn]], [[Quinn (musician)|quinn]], [[Glaive (musician)|glaive]], [[ericdoa]], [[quannnic]], [[midwxst]], [[Lucy Bedroque]] and [[brakence]].
